, 1931, Miscellanea epigrafica","Libertini, 1981, Scritti su Catania antica","Notizie degli scavi di antichità, 1876-","Ferrua, 1989, Note e giunte alle iscrizioni cristiane antiche della Sicilia","Ferrua, 1938, Osservazioni sulle iscrizioni cristiane catanesi",[237,238,239,240,239,241,242],"2EUC82DH","T67M4XMU","ZJ65DX74","4MCP2PVV","759ZXHKQ","BPRRV8SB",[244,245,246,21,26,30,247,248,249,250,248,251,252,122],"isic003284","epitaph for kyriake",{"_":5},"catina","catania","sicilia","sicily","museo civico di catania","ancient greek",[],{"title":255,"body":256,"divs":257,"editions":284,"images":294,"handnote":300},"ISic003284. Epitaph for Kyriake","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-text=\"καὶ\">κ(αὶ?)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">Κυριακή\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"καὶ\">Κ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">ΚΥΡΙΑΚΗ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003284_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003284_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003284.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003284-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Ferrua, Korhonen: κ(αὶ)\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… and Kyriake.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>... e Kyriake.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The fragment is probably part of a Christian epitaph: \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Κυριακή\u003C/span> must have been the name of the deceased (perhaps not the only one mentioned in the epitaph if \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κ\u003C/span> is an abbreviation for \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">καί\u003C/span> as in IMusCatania 167 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001648\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001648\u003C/a>) and not the indication of the day of Sunday (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κυριακὴ [ἡμήρα]\u003C/span>), as Ferrua believed. This is the only occurrence of this name in Catania, whereas it is more widespread in Christian inscriptions from Syracuse (see LGPN 3A: 262).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Libertini 1931 43 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini NSA 1931 370 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1938 70 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1981 93 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1981 113 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1989 110 no.420 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 180 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Irregular letters, A with serifs and straight bar.\u003C/p> Lines 1-2  37-42  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[258,261,264,267,270,272,275,278,281],{"id":259,"html":260},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-text=\"καὶ\">κ(αὶ?)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">Κυριακή\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"καὶ\">Κ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">ΚΥΡΙΑΚΗ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":262,"html":263},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003284_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003284_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003284.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003284-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":265,"html":266},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Ferrua, Korhonen: κ(αὶ)\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":268,"html":269},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… and Kyriake.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":268,"html":271},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>... e Kyriake.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":273,"html":274},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The fragment is probably part of a Christian epitaph: \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Κυριακή\u003C/span> must have been the name of the deceased (perhaps not the only one mentioned in the epitaph if \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κ\u003C/span> is an abbreviation for \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">καί\u003C/span> as in IMusCatania 167 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001648\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001648\u003C/a>) and not the indication of the day of Sunday (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">κυριακὴ [ἡμήρα]\u003C/span>), as Ferrua believed. This is the only occurrence of this name in Catania, whereas it is more widespread in Christian inscriptions from Syracuse (see LGPN 3A: 262).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":276,"html":277},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Libertini 1931 43 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini NSA 1931 370 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1938 70 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1981 93 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1981 113 no.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001863\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1989 110 no.420 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 180 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":279,"html":280},"handnote","\u003Cp>Irregular letters, A with serifs and straight bar.\u003C/p> Lines 1-2  37-42  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":282,"html":283},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[285,287,290,291],{"html":286},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou",{"id":288,"lang":122,"html":289},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan data-text=\"καὶ\">κ(αὶ?)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριακή\">Κυριακή\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":286},{"id":292,"lang":122,"html":293},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Α\u003Cbr 